WEBVTT

00:00:08.425 --> 00:00:10.927
<i>Princess!</i>

00:00:22.272 --> 00:00:23.940
Does it torment you

00:00:24.024 --> 00:00:27.068
To know of the bloodshed your family caused 30 years ago?

00:00:27.152 --> 00:00:31.031
Do you despise your parents so deeply that you offer your body to a spirit?

00:00:32.532 --> 00:00:34.325
<i>Your mother came to see me.</i>

00:00:34.409 --> 00:00:36.661
She pleaded with me to save her daughter.

00:00:47.756 --> 00:00:51.176
<i>I have also heard about your father.</i>

00:00:55.180 --> 00:00:58.224
<i>How could a mere court lady</i> <i>refuse an order?</i>

00:00:59.601 --> 00:01:01.895
<i>Royal Noble Consort Sukbin Choi</i> <i>forced her to do it.</i>

00:01:07.734 --> 00:01:10.904
Your father saved your mother by marrying her.

00:01:10.987 --> 00:01:13.740
So do not hate your mother or father too deeply!

00:01:15.408 --> 00:01:19.537
Do not let the spirit of the Crown Prince use that hatred!

00:01:20.789 --> 00:01:21.873
<i>Princess!</i>

00:01:23.583 --> 00:01:24.626
<i>Princess!</i>

00:01:25.460 --> 00:01:26.336
<i>Princess.</i>

00:01:27.378 --> 00:01:28.880
What are you looking at?

00:01:31.549 --> 00:01:34.636
Are these yellow flowers from the ginger tree?

00:01:34.719 --> 00:01:36.012
Yes, they are.

00:01:36.930 --> 00:01:39.265
There are many in my hometown.

00:01:40.058 --> 00:01:44.729
I told His Majesty of it, and he chose it as your childhood name.

00:01:47.482 --> 00:01:50.110
Do you miss your hometown, Mother?

00:01:50.193 --> 00:01:51.736
No.

00:01:53.071 --> 00:01:54.864
I have no fond memories there.

00:01:55.573 --> 00:01:57.784
My father died young,

00:01:58.284 --> 00:02:00.245
And my mother was always ill.

00:02:03.414 --> 00:02:04.791
Then, Mother,

00:02:05.458 --> 00:02:08.169
Be my daughter in the next life.

00:02:09.129 --> 00:02:10.797
I will keep you safe.

00:02:16.469 --> 00:02:18.763
That is a wonderful idea.

00:02:39.033 --> 00:02:40.034
What in the world

00:02:41.744 --> 00:02:42.954
- Your leg - Your Highness!

00:02:44.289 --> 00:02:45.248
Are you all right?

00:02:45.331 --> 00:02:46.791
- Are you all right? - Anyone there?

00:02:46.875 --> 00:02:48.626
- Are you all right? - Is anyone there?

00:02:48.710 --> 00:02:49.752
We need to press on it!

00:02:49.836 --> 00:02:52.547
- Your Highness, are you all right? - Check outside.

00:02:53.047 --> 00:02:54.841
- Now! - Yes, Your Majesty.

00:02:55.717 --> 00:02:58.636
Where are you going, Your Highness?

00:03:00.305 --> 00:03:01.139
Sir.

00:03:07.604 --> 00:03:08.521
What's the matter?

00:03:20.074 --> 00:03:21.409
Are you all right?

00:03:23.828 --> 00:03:26.164
Can you see now? How

00:03:26.247 --> 00:03:27.665
Let us stop the bleeding first.

00:03:34.172 --> 00:03:35.173
That was close.

00:03:35.256 --> 00:03:38.885
It was fortunate that the spirit of the Crown Prince fled when you awoke.

00:03:40.762 --> 00:03:42.472
I was a fool.

00:03:43.223 --> 00:03:44.849
I let the spirit

00:03:45.350 --> 00:03:47.018
Use my body

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:48.811
To pass the ward.

00:03:48.895 --> 00:03:50.730
Let us go to the physician first.

00:03:54.317 --> 00:03:55.276
Before that,

00:03:57.111 --> 00:03:59.030
Where is my mother?

00:04:00.865 --> 00:04:02.200
I wish to see her.

00:04:03.034 --> 00:04:05.578
I must tell her that I will release her resentment

00:04:05.662 --> 00:04:10.250
So she may pass on to the afterlife without worry.

00:04:11.751 --> 00:04:13.086
That will not be possible.

00:04:15.004 --> 00:04:16.714
- It is possible. - No, it is not.

00:04:17.465 --> 00:04:19.509
Her soul was taken by a gwi-mae.

00:04:21.386 --> 00:04:22.303
What?

00:04:23.930 --> 00:04:28.977
- What does that-- - Your mother's soul has perished.

00:04:43.616 --> 00:04:45.326
Go to Saeng-gang!

00:04:45.827 --> 00:04:47.078
I will be fine,

00:04:47.662 --> 00:04:51.374
So please protect my daughter, Saeng-gang!

00:04:58.214 --> 00:04:59.507
I am sorry.

00:06:17.251 --> 00:06:22.173
THE EAST PALACE

00:06:23.591 --> 00:06:26.094
The Princess came to see me last night.

00:06:27.303 --> 00:06:28.971
The eunuchs told me

00:06:29.722 --> 00:06:31.933
That she was acting strangely.

00:06:32.016 --> 00:06:33.184
It is nothing.

00:06:33.267 --> 00:06:35.144
There is no need for concern.

00:06:36.437 --> 00:06:39.524
More importantly, I must go outside the palace.

00:06:39.607 --> 00:06:42.485
- For the Crown Prince's soul to pass-- - There is no need.

00:06:42.568 --> 00:06:46.447
Do not send it to the afterlife. Destroy it.

00:06:49.659 --> 00:06:51.369
Do you understand what it means

00:06:52.787 --> 00:06:54.288
To destroy a soul?

00:06:54.372 --> 00:06:55.331
It matters not.

00:06:55.415 --> 00:06:58.376
In any case, you cannot leave.

00:06:59.293 --> 00:07:01.963
- Leave outside matters to the Princess. - No.

00:07:02.046 --> 00:07:04.507
I will tell the Princess to step away from this matter.

00:07:04.590 --> 00:07:05.967
It is too dangerous.

00:07:07.343 --> 00:07:09.220
You said it was nothing.

00:07:15.601 --> 00:07:18.688
So something has happened to the Princess.

00:07:19.188 --> 00:07:20.523
And

00:07:23.943 --> 00:07:26.195
Something has happened to you as well.

00:07:35.872 --> 00:07:39.000
I summoned the Princess because she can hear spirits.

00:07:39.667 --> 00:07:41.502
She may be of use,

00:07:42.003 --> 00:07:43.421
So work with her.

00:07:43.504 --> 00:07:46.132
I clearly told you the Princess was in danger.

00:07:46.215 --> 00:07:49.260
It is not your place to concern yourself with her safety.

00:07:49.343 --> 00:07:53.806
Or have you forgotten your lowly status and dared to set your heart on her?

00:07:56.434 --> 00:07:57.643
Of course not.

00:07:59.729 --> 00:08:01.481
I only mean to stop her

00:08:02.190 --> 00:08:03.524
Because she is in the way.

00:08:05.193 --> 00:08:08.029
As she gets closer to the truth about the Crown Prince's spirit,

00:08:08.905 --> 00:08:11.741
She learns of Your Majesty and the royal family's shame.

00:08:12.408 --> 00:08:14.952
And it is becoming harder for her to bear.

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:40.436
Why are you still here?

00:08:42.980 --> 00:08:44.982
In case you get possessed again.

00:08:53.616 --> 00:08:55.076
Tell me now.

00:08:55.660 --> 00:08:58.287
How did you regain your sight?

00:09:00.623 --> 00:09:02.124
I gained the eyes of a gwi-mae.

00:09:02.208 --> 00:09:03.334
The eyes of a gwi-mae?

00:09:03.417 --> 00:09:05.795
What happens to you, then?

00:09:07.296 --> 00:09:10.299
Well, do not concern yourself with that. Just keep this well.

00:09:11.050 --> 00:09:12.718
Do not lose it.

00:09:13.803 --> 00:09:16.973
Do not concern yourself with the spirit of the Crown Prince as well.

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:19.141
Now that I have my sight back,

00:09:20.101 --> 00:09:21.978
I will deal with spirits alone.

00:09:22.061 --> 00:09:23.229
Why all of a sudden--

00:09:23.312 --> 00:09:24.730
Because you get in the way.

00:09:27.817 --> 00:09:30.695
The spirit of the Crown Prince might take over your body again.

00:09:33.406 --> 00:09:36.242
I am at my wit's end cleaning up after you.

00:09:36.325 --> 00:09:37.368
Gu-cheon.

00:09:50.131 --> 00:09:51.841
Is this because of my mother?

00:09:53.759 --> 00:09:55.136
If that is the reason

00:09:57.471 --> 00:09:58.806
Do not concern yourself.

00:10:00.141 --> 00:10:02.435
She met her end trying to save me,

00:10:02.935 --> 00:10:04.687
So you have nothing to be sorry for.

00:10:05.813 --> 00:10:07.607
It is not your fault.

00:10:10.109 --> 00:10:12.194
- Do you hear me? - It is my fault.

00:10:15.114 --> 00:10:16.324
Once before

00:10:18.618 --> 00:10:21.871
A gwi-mae was after my Yin energy, and I let it devour a soul.

00:10:23.706 --> 00:10:26.292
So you should stay away from me.

00:10:27.293 --> 00:10:30.588
You never know what might happen if you stay with a cursed man like me.

00:11:02.995 --> 00:11:04.580
<i>I will not lose anyone</i>

00:11:05.748 --> 00:11:08.125
<i>because of me again.</i>

00:11:13.714 --> 00:11:16.300
Did you bring those wards from your residence?

00:11:18.469 --> 00:11:19.637
That is quite a lot.

00:11:20.304 --> 00:11:21.722
You may all leave.

00:11:22.306 --> 00:11:23.766
- Yes. - Yes.

00:11:28.813 --> 00:11:32.191
Where did you go last night?

00:11:33.567 --> 00:11:34.902
Come here.

00:11:35.653 --> 00:11:36.612
Come now.

00:11:37.905 --> 00:11:39.824
Come, dear.

00:11:45.287 --> 00:11:50.668
You must be my dearest granddaughter again.

00:11:50.751 --> 00:11:51.711
And

00:11:52.253 --> 00:11:54.547
Let us keep the secret of 30 years ago

00:11:55.047 --> 00:11:58.134
And protect our family together.

00:12:01.303 --> 00:12:04.598
Someone has already begun to notice.

00:12:06.350 --> 00:12:07.601
Your Highness.

00:12:07.685 --> 00:12:10.688
The Queen Dowager urgently requests your presence at her residence.

00:12:13.649 --> 00:12:15.860
His Majesty the King has arrived.

00:12:41.093 --> 00:12:42.303
You may all be seated.

00:12:49.101 --> 00:12:51.312
You even summoned the royal relatives.

00:12:51.395 --> 00:12:53.814
What did you wish to see me about so urgently?

00:12:54.315 --> 00:12:57.067
I have no leisure to enjoy refreshments.

00:12:57.151 --> 00:12:59.153
Thirty years ago,

00:13:00.738 --> 00:13:04.366
When the late King's sons met their untimely deaths,

00:13:05.201 --> 00:13:09.830
You were the only one to survive. Why?

00:13:16.587 --> 00:13:18.339
Has my survival

00:13:20.007 --> 00:13:23.427
Displeased you all this time, Mother?

00:13:23.511 --> 00:13:29.391
I ask how you escaped the curse of the pond spirit.

00:13:29.475 --> 00:13:32.895
At the time, I took refuge in the temple of a monk known for exorcisms.

00:13:32.978 --> 00:13:35.898
- You already knew, did you not? - No!

00:13:36.690 --> 00:13:38.776
There was no need.

00:13:39.276 --> 00:13:41.737
Because the pond spirit never existed to begin with.

00:13:43.197 --> 00:13:47.243
The deaths of the Princes 30 years ago were not the work of the pond spirit.

00:13:47.326 --> 00:13:49.036
This was clearly

00:13:49.662 --> 00:13:52.665
Poisoning by human hands.

00:13:52.748 --> 00:13:54.917
Bring him in!

00:14:07.888 --> 00:14:11.308
Prince Inha collapsed as soon as he entered the palace.

00:14:11.809 --> 00:14:15.062
And something was found in his quarters.

00:14:19.358 --> 00:14:22.194
The refreshment box Prince Inha ate from.

00:14:22.862 --> 00:14:24.530
And there is another.

00:14:25.447 --> 00:14:27.992
The one the Princess gave me.

00:14:28.993 --> 00:14:33.497
I heard her mother died after eating from that lotus-patterned box as well.

00:14:33.998 --> 00:14:38.377
This clearly proves the Princes were not killed by the pond spirit

00:14:38.460 --> 00:14:41.589
But were poisoned.

00:14:42.631 --> 00:14:44.675
What do you think, Your Majesty?

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:49.221
Are you saying

00:14:51.765 --> 00:14:55.477
That I killed my own brothers?

00:14:55.561 --> 00:15:00.649
When everyone else is killed, the sole survivor is the culprit.

00:15:01.150 --> 00:15:03.152
I speak of Your Majesty,

00:15:03.235 --> 00:15:06.864
Who could never have risen to the throne otherwise.

00:15:07.364 --> 00:15:09.867
What you just said

00:15:12.786 --> 00:15:15.331
Can you bear what you have said?

00:15:34.850 --> 00:15:36.518
What do you think you are doing?

00:15:42.566 --> 00:15:43.776
Your Majesty.

00:16:53.721 --> 00:16:55.305
You said it was poison.

00:16:55.389 --> 00:16:57.850
We shall see in time.

00:17:01.228 --> 00:17:02.187
Oh, right.

00:17:04.023 --> 00:17:06.442
- Chief Eunuch Kim. - Yes, Your Majesty.

00:17:08.902 --> 00:17:12.740
- Take Prince Inha outside the palace now. - Take him outside the palace?

00:17:15.075 --> 00:17:16.910
There is something I wish to see.

00:17:19.538 --> 00:17:21.081
Stop!

00:17:29.465 --> 00:17:30.340
Your Majesty.

00:17:31.300 --> 00:17:35.179
Prince Inha awoke the moment he left the palace.

00:17:35.262 --> 00:17:36.138
What?

00:17:36.638 --> 00:17:39.224
And he asked that a message be delivered.

00:17:39.308 --> 00:17:41.935
What? What did he say?

00:17:42.853 --> 00:17:44.730
A spirit tried to kill him.

00:17:45.856 --> 00:17:48.525
He said that it would wipe out the royal bloodline.

00:17:49.234 --> 00:17:50.944
That cannot be.

00:17:51.028 --> 00:17:53.280
He was clearly poisoned.

00:17:53.363 --> 00:17:54.406
Poisoned?

00:17:54.490 --> 00:17:57.159
How can you say such a ridiculous thing?

00:17:57.659 --> 00:18:03.373
Are you saying I killed my own sons with my own hands?

00:18:06.835 --> 00:18:09.171
They were all killed by the pond spirit.

00:18:10.339 --> 00:18:14.051
I speak of the Most Favored Lady of the Court you killed.

00:18:14.551 --> 00:18:15.677
No.

00:18:17.471 --> 00:18:19.431
I hesitated because you were unwell.

00:18:19.515 --> 00:18:22.267
But I have no choice now.

00:18:22.351 --> 00:18:28.273
You brutally killed that pregnant lady and cut off the royal bloodline.

00:18:28.357 --> 00:18:33.195
You even dared brand me, the King of this land, a murderer!

00:18:33.278 --> 00:18:35.823
I will tolerate this no longer!

00:18:39.076 --> 00:18:40.786
Leave the palace.

00:18:42.079 --> 00:18:43.163
At once.

00:19:00.430 --> 00:19:03.142
How dare you!

00:19:03.892 --> 00:19:06.061
I already know the truth!

00:19:06.145 --> 00:19:09.773
This was all your doing! I know it all!

00:19:10.357 --> 00:19:12.151
I know everything!

00:19:12.651 --> 00:19:14.403
I know it all, you wretch!

00:19:20.450 --> 00:19:22.119
No, you are wrong.

00:19:23.787 --> 00:19:25.247
It was you.

00:19:26.456 --> 00:19:29.668
It was you who started

00:19:30.919 --> 00:19:32.254
All this curse and tragedy.

00:19:32.337 --> 00:19:34.173
You are the one

00:19:34.923 --> 00:19:38.093
Who dragged me into this hell.

00:19:38.177 --> 00:19:40.304
All because of you.

00:19:42.181 --> 00:19:44.975
It is time you accept it.

00:19:45.601 --> 00:19:46.643
This is

00:19:50.772 --> 00:19:52.733
Your retribution.

00:19:54.234 --> 00:19:55.527
Mother.

00:20:13.921 --> 00:20:17.090
I will never leave.

00:20:18.425 --> 00:20:21.970
This palace belongs to me!

00:20:22.054 --> 00:20:25.182
I will not leave, even in death!

00:20:25.265 --> 00:20:27.893
I will never leave!

00:20:27.976 --> 00:20:31.230
This palace is mine!

00:20:31.313 --> 00:20:35.067
- Your Majesty, are you all right? - It is mine!

00:20:35.150 --> 00:20:36.151
Your Majesty.

00:20:38.111 --> 00:20:39.363
Father!

00:20:45.786 --> 00:20:46.954
Let us leave.

00:20:55.879 --> 00:20:58.090
Did you even use the spirit of the Crown Prince?

00:20:58.799 --> 00:21:01.677
Knowing the spirit would harm him, you took Prince Inha in.

00:21:02.344 --> 00:21:04.012
How could you

00:21:04.096 --> 00:21:05.973
You are the one who is out of your mind.

00:21:06.807 --> 00:21:09.184
And who are you today?

00:21:11.103 --> 00:21:12.562
Are you truly the Princess?

00:21:15.023 --> 00:21:17.985
Do not appear before me until the pond spirit is destroyed.

00:21:18.068 --> 00:21:19.945
I cannot trust you.

00:21:20.028 --> 00:21:22.990
I cannot trust you either, Father.

00:21:27.077 --> 00:21:30.163
Why did your first and second sons die, Father?

00:21:31.373 --> 00:21:32.749
Like your third son,

00:21:33.959 --> 00:21:35.627
Did you poison them as well?

00:21:37.421 --> 00:21:39.256
The consequences of that sin

00:21:40.841 --> 00:21:42.968
Will surely come upon you.

00:21:48.432 --> 00:21:49.349
Very well.

00:21:51.977 --> 00:21:53.186
I will be waiting.

00:22:02.154 --> 00:22:07.367
I must kill the King.

00:22:07.868 --> 00:22:09.328
The King

00:22:10.495 --> 00:22:14.750
I must kill the King.

00:22:17.044 --> 00:22:18.503
You may enter.

00:22:31.892 --> 00:22:34.561
<i>Are you saying the pestilence</i> <i>is near the capital?</i>

00:22:34.644 --> 00:22:36.146
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

00:22:36.229 --> 00:22:38.106
All gates to the capital are closed,

00:22:38.190 --> 00:22:40.567
And the people are barred from entering or leaving.

00:22:42.235 --> 00:22:45.030
Jeonuigam, Hyeminseo, and Hwalinseo.

00:22:45.113 --> 00:22:49.034
Find a way to stop the pestilence and report to me.

00:22:49.117 --> 00:22:52.746
And the Ministry of Taxation. Release the stored grain--

00:22:53.663 --> 00:22:54.831
Your Majesty.

00:23:01.713 --> 00:23:02.631
Your Majesty.

00:23:03.673 --> 00:23:05.300
The pestilence has reached you.

00:23:05.926 --> 00:23:08.428
- I will summon the royal physician. - No.

00:23:12.557 --> 00:23:13.433
Gu-cheon.

00:23:15.727 --> 00:23:17.771
Gu-cheon. Bring him here.

00:23:18.271 --> 00:23:19.189
Now.

00:23:24.653 --> 00:23:25.779
Your Majesty.

00:23:27.322 --> 00:23:29.116
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

00:23:29.616 --> 00:23:30.909
- Your Majesty. - Your Majesty.

00:23:30.992 --> 00:23:32.119
Your Majesty!

00:23:33.328 --> 00:23:35.163
Take a good look at me.

00:23:43.088 --> 00:23:44.714
What do you see?

00:23:46.758 --> 00:23:50.011
Something different from the spirits I usually see in the palace.

00:23:50.095 --> 00:23:53.849
- I see the people wailing. - My lord.

00:23:54.516 --> 00:23:56.977
- Please help us. - Spots are all over their bodies

00:23:57.060 --> 00:24:00.856
- There is a child of Prince Yeongan's age. - My lord, please help us.

00:24:00.939 --> 00:24:03.567
She is holding onto Your Majesty's robe.

00:24:06.528 --> 00:24:08.196
They are the people you killed

00:24:10.365 --> 00:24:12.534
In the village affected by the pestilence.

00:24:13.243 --> 00:24:17.747
Are you saying they came to the palace with resentment against me?

00:24:18.248 --> 00:24:19.958
Won-gwi are quite simple.

00:24:20.041 --> 00:24:24.045
If they bore resentment, they would seek the soldiers who killed them.

00:24:26.339 --> 00:24:28.967
Yet they came for Your Majesty, who gave the order.

00:24:30.010 --> 00:24:32.095
As though someone guided them here.

00:24:34.222 --> 00:24:37.017
Then the one who brought them into the palace must be

00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:44.941
The spirit of the Crown Prince.

00:24:56.578 --> 00:24:59.873
Then go and see it done.

00:25:02.501 --> 00:25:04.503
Then what will you do with them?

00:25:05.629 --> 00:25:08.131
If you leave them be, Your Majesty will be in danger.

00:25:08.715 --> 00:25:10.133
An appeasement rite.

00:25:11.301 --> 00:25:13.303
I will perform the rite tomorrow night

00:25:14.179 --> 00:25:16.556
To drive out the pestilent-gwis.

00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:18.058
Drive them out?

00:25:19.434 --> 00:25:24.481
That mindset will not do. The rite appeases the wronged souls.

00:25:24.564 --> 00:25:29.569
- Such an approach will only fail. - Just focus on the Crown Prince's spirit.

00:25:31.154 --> 00:25:33.782
The time we agreed upon is near.

00:26:22.622 --> 00:26:23.915
What are you doing?

00:26:24.416 --> 00:26:25.500
It is calling

00:26:26.251 --> 00:26:27.335
Me.

00:26:30.755 --> 00:26:31.715
Who?

00:26:35.552 --> 00:26:36.428
Gu-cheon.

00:26:38.555 --> 00:26:39.723
It is nothing.

00:26:42.142 --> 00:26:43.184
Tell me.

00:26:43.268 --> 00:26:46.313
Has your condition worsened since you gained the eyes of gwi-mae?

00:26:46.396 --> 00:26:48.273
More importantly, why are you here?

00:26:49.316 --> 00:26:51.693
I told you I would handle the spirit alone.

00:26:56.072 --> 00:26:57.532
Must you be like this?

00:26:59.618 --> 00:27:04.289
I told you my mother's soul perished because of me being possessed, not you.

00:27:10.587 --> 00:27:13.089
I know this is all out of concern for me.

00:27:14.299 --> 00:27:16.426
What has happened

00:27:17.302 --> 00:27:19.054
And what will happen

00:27:20.055 --> 00:27:21.765
Are all mine to bear.

00:27:22.265 --> 00:27:23.683
Not yours.

00:27:30.565 --> 00:27:33.068
<i>The Crown Prince's spirit</i> <i>failed to reach the King.</i>

00:27:34.527 --> 00:27:37.113
<i>Now it is drawing in the pestilent-gwis.</i>

00:27:37.197 --> 00:27:39.699
I will draw them all in.

00:27:39.783 --> 00:27:41.785
<i>The spirit of the Crown Prince</i>

00:27:42.952 --> 00:27:44.913
<i>will surely try to kill the King.</i>

00:27:47.165 --> 00:27:48.625
<i>Draw them in</i>

00:27:50.293 --> 00:27:52.754
<i>I could not even protect</i> <i>your mother's soul.</i>

00:27:54.422 --> 00:27:56.758
So I cannot let your father die as well.

00:28:02.389 --> 00:28:05.058
I should send you out of the palace at once,

00:28:05.975 --> 00:28:07.769
But I cannot for now.

00:28:08.978 --> 00:28:10.772
You are the only one I can rely on.

00:28:14.526 --> 00:28:16.820
Let us wait until sunrise

00:28:17.696 --> 00:28:19.322
So I can replenish my Yang energy.

00:28:34.421 --> 00:28:36.715
I will share my Yang energy with you.

00:29:06.953 --> 00:29:09.956
<i>I will find out what the pestilent-gwis</i> <i>will be used for.</i>

00:29:10.832 --> 00:29:13.877
<i>In the meantime,</i> <i>you should buy me some time.</i>

00:29:16.004 --> 00:29:17.839
<i>Write the protective sutra,</i>

00:29:17.922 --> 00:29:20.800
<i>coat it with chicken blood,</i> <i>and put it in the King's bedchamber.</i>

00:29:23.344 --> 00:29:26.681
<i>That way, the Crown Prince</i> <i>will not be able to approach easily.</i>

00:29:29.267 --> 00:29:32.937
<i>The King must be protected</i> <i>until the appeasement rite.</i>

00:29:39.611 --> 00:29:40.945
What are you doing?

00:29:41.029 --> 00:29:43.448
From now on, do not let anyone enter this chamber.

00:30:00.799 --> 00:30:02.217
I asked you what you are doing.

00:30:02.300 --> 00:30:04.511
- Why are you here? - I did not wish to come either.

00:30:04.594 --> 00:30:08.515
But I was told I must protect you until the appeasement rite.

00:30:11.684 --> 00:30:13.895
So that is what Gu-cheon said.

00:30:18.733 --> 00:30:21.277
<i>I must tell you something, Your Majesty.</i>

00:30:22.904 --> 00:30:23.863
What is the matter?

00:30:25.698 --> 00:30:29.911
Something is here, but not a pestilent-gwi.

00:30:30.703 --> 00:30:31.746
Your Majesty.

00:30:32.789 --> 00:30:33.748
Behind you, Father

00:30:36.501 --> 00:30:38.419
I must tell you about the Crown Prince.

00:30:39.003 --> 00:30:39.879
Stop there.

00:30:39.963 --> 00:30:42.924
Please hear me out, Your Majesty.

00:30:45.969 --> 00:30:48.805
- He is about to speak of the Crown Prince. - Please

00:30:48.888 --> 00:30:50.849
No. Do not listen to him.

00:30:50.932 --> 00:30:53.935
- Please hear me out. - What else are you trying to hide?

00:30:54.727 --> 00:30:57.230
- Leave at once. Now! - No.

00:30:57.856 --> 00:31:02.151
- Say it yourself. You cannot avoid it now. - That is enough, Saeng-gang!

00:31:02.235 --> 00:31:05.196
I must hear that spirit's plea.

00:31:05.280 --> 00:31:07.073
- Please - I must know what it has to say.

00:31:09.409 --> 00:31:11.828
Do not come closer. Do not listen to it.

00:31:11.911 --> 00:31:14.038
Do not try to find out anything more!

00:31:14.122 --> 00:31:14.956
Leave at once!

00:31:15.039 --> 00:31:17.584
- I said leave at once! - Father!

00:31:47.447 --> 00:31:48.698
Who is he?

00:31:50.241 --> 00:31:53.703
Did you kill him as well, Father?

00:31:56.122 --> 00:31:57.081
Yes, I did.

00:31:59.709 --> 00:32:01.628
Why did you kill him?

00:32:05.089 --> 00:32:06.549
He

00:32:12.680 --> 00:32:14.849
He was about to speak of

00:32:20.021 --> 00:32:21.731
What the Crown Prince had done.

00:32:33.493 --> 00:32:34.535
I see.

00:32:38.915 --> 00:32:40.875
This palace has always been

00:32:41.751 --> 00:32:43.336
Quite an interesting place.

00:32:45.546 --> 00:32:46.839
Is that not so?

00:32:55.390 --> 00:32:56.808
Are you saying

00:32:57.767 --> 00:33:00.561
The Crown Prince could hear the spirits as well?

00:33:18.121 --> 00:33:19.414
Tell me

00:33:19.914 --> 00:33:22.709
How I became King.

00:33:29.549 --> 00:33:35.221
- The late King's Princes died one by one-- - And what about the Princes?

00:33:37.640 --> 00:33:39.225
Tell me how they died.

00:33:42.812 --> 00:33:44.605
I heard it was the pond spirit's curse.

00:33:47.984 --> 00:33:49.694
Tell me the truth.

00:33:51.279 --> 00:33:53.197
I do not understand what you mean

00:33:53.281 --> 00:33:56.993
In my mother's bloodline,

00:33:57.076 --> 00:34:01.998
Some children are born with a cursed gift passed down through generations.

00:34:02.081 --> 00:34:04.083
You are one of them.

00:34:05.793 --> 00:34:10.923
Since you can hear the spirits, you must have known long ago

00:34:11.007 --> 00:34:13.259
That the pond spirit was never real.

00:34:13.342 --> 00:34:16.471
And that it was not a spirit that killed the late King's Princes

00:34:20.183 --> 00:34:22.310
But a human.

00:34:26.481 --> 00:34:27.482
Father!

00:34:27.565 --> 00:34:28.566
And yet

00:34:29.067 --> 00:34:32.612
My first and second sons died.

00:34:33.112 --> 00:34:36.657
Even though the pond spirit was never real.

00:34:37.325 --> 00:34:40.953
They coughed up black blood as my brothers did.

00:34:42.789 --> 00:34:43.831
You

00:34:45.541 --> 00:34:49.295
Must have heard of the secret from 30 years ago

00:34:50.046 --> 00:34:51.923
And recreated it.

00:35:02.350 --> 00:35:05.144
Did you think I would spare you?

00:35:20.034 --> 00:35:21.035
Did you truly

00:35:23.871 --> 00:35:25.957
Put poison in the tea?

00:35:33.047 --> 00:35:34.715
How could a father

00:35:35.216 --> 00:35:38.094
Kill his own child with his own hands?

00:35:38.177 --> 00:35:41.514
You should not become King and rule the people.

00:35:42.014 --> 00:35:44.183
You must never become King.

00:35:44.267 --> 00:35:45.351
Why?

00:35:46.602 --> 00:35:49.438
You became King that way, so why?

00:35:50.148 --> 00:35:53.151
Why can I not?

00:36:11.252 --> 00:36:14.172
One man who killed his brothers to become King is enough.

00:36:15.423 --> 00:36:17.717
And that man is me.

00:36:20.845 --> 00:36:22.013
You, too

00:36:24.891 --> 00:36:27.768
Will be said to have died from the curse of the pond spirit.

00:36:29.896 --> 00:36:31.939
Yes, do as you wish.

00:36:50.374 --> 00:36:53.461
Since you are the pond spirit,

00:36:55.004 --> 00:36:58.382
It is only fitting that a spirit kill me as well.

00:37:03.971 --> 00:37:05.723
And I will die

00:37:10.144 --> 00:37:14.232
And become the true pond spirit for you.

00:37:26.327 --> 00:37:28.537
Father!

00:37:33.709 --> 00:37:37.421
As the curse said 30 years ago

00:37:41.592 --> 00:37:47.014
I will cut off the royal bloodline.

00:37:50.268 --> 00:37:54.772
If I cannot become King

00:38:03.614 --> 00:38:04.657
Father.

00:38:15.418 --> 00:38:16.419
Father.

00:38:16.919 --> 00:38:17.920
Father!

00:38:21.966 --> 00:38:26.887
<i>You cannot be King either, Father.</i>

00:38:58.085 --> 00:39:02.757
May peace and prosperity fill this household!

00:39:02.840 --> 00:39:07.136
With one heart, we offer our solemn prayers!

00:39:07.720 --> 00:39:12.141
Your Highness, the Crown Prince, guardian deity of the palace!

00:39:12.224 --> 00:39:14.518
Accept this humble offering

00:39:14.602 --> 00:39:19.190
And drive the pestilent-gwis out of the palace!

00:39:30.076 --> 00:39:32.328
Is he devouring human souls like a gwi-mae?

00:39:32.912 --> 00:39:34.705
Stop it!

00:40:24.130 --> 00:40:25.131
Your Majesty!

00:40:30.594 --> 00:40:32.012
Is His Majesty

00:40:34.598 --> 00:40:35.891
Dead?

00:40:36.392 --> 00:40:37.560
Father.

00:40:38.060 --> 00:40:39.103
Father!

00:40:50.614 --> 00:40:51.907
Gu-cheon!

00:44:18.656 --> 00:44:21.867
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang

